# 🚀 CustomerOS AI

## Overview

CustomerOS AI is an AI-powered Customer Success, Product Analytics, Business Intelligence, and Predictive Analytics platform designed to help SaaS companies understand customer health, reduce churn, prioritize product decisions, and drive business growth.

The platform combines operational workflows, analytics, machine learning, and AI-driven insights into a single unified system.

---

# 🎯 Project Vision

Build an end-to-end customer intelligence platform that demonstrates:

* Product Management
* AI Product Management
* Product Analytics
* Data Analytics
* Business Analytics
* Customer Success Operations
* Business Intelligence
* Applied Machine Learning

---

# 🗺️ Product Roadmap

## Phase 1: Customer Success Platform ✅

Core business workflows and operational intelligence.

### Features

* Authentication & Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)
* Customer Accounts Management
* Feedback Management
* Support Ticket Management
* Risk Flag Tracking
* Account Health Scoring
* Feature Request Management
* Product Roadmap Planning

### Demonstrates

* Product Management
* Customer Success Operations
* SaaS Workflow Design

---

## Phase 2: AI Intelligence Layer ✅

AI-powered decision support and customer intelligence.

### Features

* AI Insights Engine
* AI Copilot
* Intent Detection
* Context Retrieval
* Natural Language Q&A

### Demonstrates

* AI Product Management
* LLM Integration
* AI-Assisted Decision Making

---

## Phase 3: Portfolio & Documentation 🚧

### Features

* GitHub README
* Product Case Study
* Architecture Diagram
* Demo Screenshots
* Technical Documentation

### Demonstrates

* Product Communication
* Product Strategy
* Stakeholder Storytelling

